@@TJvStarfield
<GROUP TJvStarfield>
Summary
  A star field with moving stars.
Description
  Use TJvStarfield to show a star field with moving stars.
  
  Use Stars to specify the amount of stars on the star field. Use MaxSpeed to limit the amount of
  pixels a star will move per refresh event. Set Delay to indicate the amount of time (in milli-seconds)
  between refresh events.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStarfield.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvStarField object.
Description
  Call Create to create an instance of TJvStarField at runtime. A TJvStarField component placed on a 
  form at design time is created automatically.

  Pass a single Component as a parameter to provide the star field with an Owner that is 
  responsible for freeing it.

  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the star field 
  as follows: 

  * Active is set to False.
  * Delay is set to 50.
  * MaxSpeed is set to 10.
  * Stars is set to 100.
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the star field.
See Also
  Active, Delay, Destroy, MaxSpeed, Stars
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStarfield.Destroy
Summary
  Destroys an instance of TJvStarField.
Description
  Do not call Destroy directly in an application. Instead, call Free. Free verifies that the 
  TJvStarfield object is not nil and only then calls Destroy.
Parameters
  None.
See Also
   Create
